  "story" = 'I built the Stormz+ mobile app as a production React Native application using Expo to extend the streaming platform to mobile devices. The app shares the same Supabase backend as the web version, ensuring seamless data synchronization across all platforms. Built with modern React Native practices including Expo Router for navigation and native performance optimizations.',
